<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - ATC AfriGlam</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="section-title">About ATC AfriGlam</h1>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/800x600" alt="African artisans creating traditional fabrics">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At ATC AfriGlam, we are dedicated to celebrating the rich heritage of African fashion. Our
                        mission is to provide authentic, high-quality apparel and accessories that reflect the vibrant
                        cultures and traditions of Africa.</p>

                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded by a group of passionate artisans and fashion enthusiasts, ATC AfriGlam was born from a
                        desire to share the beauty of African craftsmanship with the world. Each piece in our collection
                        tells a unique story, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design.</p>

                    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
                    <div class="icon-list">
                        <div class="icon-item">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M12 8v4l3 3m-3-3H9m3-4a4 4 0 100 8 4 4 0 000-8z" />
                            </svg>
                            <p>Ethical Fashion</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="icon-item">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M3 3h18v18H3V3z" />
                            </svg>
                            <p>Quality Craftsmanship</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="icon-item">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
                            </svg>
                            <p>Community Support</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2>Our Values</h2>
                    <p>We value authenticity, quality, and sustainability. Our products are crafted with care, ensuring
                        that each item is not only beautiful but also made to last. We are committed to transparency in
                        our sourcing and production processes, allowing our customers to feel good about their
                        purchases.</p>

                    <h2>Join Us on Our Journey</h2>
                    <p>We invite you to explore our collections and discover the stories behind each piece. By choosing
                        ATC AfriGlam, you are joining a community that celebrates diversity, creativity, and the rich
                        tapestry of African culture.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Newsletter Section -->
    <section class="newsletter">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Stay Connected</h2>
            <p class="newsletter-subtitle">Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive updates, promotions, and fashion
                tips!</p>
            <form class="newsletter-form">
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required>
                <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Subscribe</button>
            </form>
            <p class="newsletter-disclaimer">*We respect your privacy. Unsubscribe at any time.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>

    <script src="script.js">
    </script>
</body>

</html>